            <!-- Process Details -->
            <div id="process" class="view">
                <h2 style="color: #2a5298; margin-bottom: 20px;">Detailed Process Workflow</h2>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h4>üîÑ Process Overview</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>System Screening:</strong> System autofills technical evaluation based on schedule of requirements and bid received</li>
                        <li><strong>Procurement Official Assignment:</strong> Assigns suppliers/materials/lots or full response tables to evaluators with instructions</li>
                        <li><strong>Collaboration with Panel:</strong> Evaluators each have column for review, can change ratings, add comments, propose clarifications - independently</li>
                        <li><strong>Review & Clarifications:</strong> PO reviews input, requests evaluation clarifications from bidders, reviews inconsistencies between ratings</li>
                        <li><strong>Compiling Input:</strong> Based on vendor clarifications and further engagement with panel, PO provides final ratings</li>
                        <li><strong>For RFPs:</strong> Instead of pass/fail, system screening is not generated</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #2a5298; margin-bottom: 15px;">üîß Key Features</h3>
                    
                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
                        <div style="background: #e7f3ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;">
                            <h4 style="color: #1976D2; margin-bottom: 10px;">üìù Capture Bidder Responses</h4>
                            <p>System automatically captures and displays bidder responses and comments on deviations</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #f3e5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #9c27b0;">
                            <h4 style="color: #7b1fa2; margin-bottom: 10px;">ü§ñ Automate Evaluation</h4>
                            <p>System generates automated pass/fail assessments based on bidder responses for review</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;">
                            <h4 style="color: #2e7d32; margin-bottom: 10px;">üìä Generate Reports</h4>
                            <p>System generates automated reports for panel review with editable fields</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;">
                            <h4 style="color: #e65100; margin-bottom: 10px;">üí¨ Comment Fields</h4>
                            <p>Include comment field for each evaluator with ability to override system ratings</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #fce4ec; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #e91e63;">
                            <h4 style="color: #c2185b; margin-bottom: 10px;">üîí Protected Comments</h4>
                            <p>Evaluators cannot remove each others' comments - ensuring independence</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #e0f2f1; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #009688;">
                            <h4 style="color: #00695c; margin-bottom: 10px;">üìã Assignment Capability</h4>
                            <p>PO can assign specific items/lots/vendors to evaluators for large complex tenders</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #f1f8e9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #8bc34a;">
                            <h4 style="color: #558b2f; margin-bottom: 10px;">üîç Compilation Matrix</h4>
                            <p>Brings in all evaluators' input, highlighting discrepancies between assessments</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: #ede7f6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #673ab7;">
                            <h4 style="color: #4527a0; margin-bottom: 10px;">‚úÖ Final Assessment</h4>
                            <p>Dedicated column for final assessment to be finalized by Procurement Official</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 40px; background: #fff9c4; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #fbc02d;">
                    <h3 style="color: #f57f17; margin-bottom: 15px;">üí° Benefits of Automated Collaboration</h3>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; line-height: 2;">
                        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Complete audit trail of all evaluator inputs and changes</li>
                        <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Reduces manual compilation and email exchanges</li>
                        <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Enables simultaneous independent reviews</li>
                        <li><strong>Consistency:</strong> System-generated preliminary screening ensures uniformity</li>
                        <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Highlights discrepancies for review and discussion</li>
                        <li><strong>Reduced Admin Burden:</strong> Automated report generation from system entries</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
